#eNCA #DStv403 eNCA's Lindokuhle Xulu has the details.  JOHANNESBURG - Back for the first time in two years. Constitution Hill has held its Human Rights Day Festival in Joburg. The event, which is open to the public, brings together individuals, artists and organisations contributing to nation-building. Organisers have expressed relief that the festival could finally take place this year. eNCA's Lindokuhle Xulu has the details in the video above.